    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Free Peoples Strategy<br />
	Get possessions/Artifacts on Durin III  to boost him up.  Get aggression down to draw cards.  If you go first play greatest kingdom of my people with your site.  Discard shadow players card off his draw deck thin your next turn use Ring of Guile to get nobody tosses a dwarf back.  Put Honed on Preparations so you can play it with Sindri’s text.  Increase damage with lord of moria,  aggression, and Ring of Fury for blood runs chill Gimli’s  and Honed.  Blood runs chill get rid of shadow conditions, possessions, and artifacts.<br />
<br />
Shadow Strategy<br />
  Morgul Hunter is for vitality, so you can get your Tower of Barad-Dur, Ithil Stone, the irresistible shadow, desperate defense of the ring, Thin and stretched, and his cruelty and malice.  Grishnakh for drawing cards or adding burdens, as well as to make the site number of the orcs mines three. Thin and stretched is to get burden for the irresistible shadow and desperate measures. Desperate defense of the ring is to discard cards or add burdens.  Tower of Barad-Dur is to discard cards from the free peoples hand every time they move.  Ithil Stone is to draw a card every shadow phase and play one minion for mines three.  <br />
<br />
